org.nzdis.micro.gip.annotations

Annotation Type GenericIntent


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface GenericIntent
    This annotation indicates that an intent is fully self-contained (i.e. holds both properties and operations for its completion. If annotated as GenericIntent, it will be processed by the platform's generic intent processor.
    Author:
    Christopher Frantz
